title: route 66 - Season 2
description:
When two friends, Tod Stiles (Martin Milner) and Buz Murdock (George Maharis), and later in Season Three, Lincoln Case (Glenn Corbett)set off across the USA in a beautiful new Corvette convertible, they never imagined the series of adventures in which they would find themselves along the often dangerous highway, iconic Route 66.  Get ready to hit the open road on Route 66!

This is a direct rip from the SF DVD, just so you know. Expect minimal pixilation/artifacts on certain episodes
